## 8-16. `src/datasystem/client/object_cache/object_client_impl.cpp` H2D/D2H 相关 9 处

先改本文件已有的 `AccessRecord(...)` helper，让它内部 lazy 计算 dataSize 和 key 字符串：

```cpp
void AccessRecord(AccessRecorder &recorder, const Status &rc,
                  const std::vector<DeviceBlobList> &blobLists,
                  const std::vector<std::string> &keys)
{
    recorder.Record(rc, [&](AccessLogFields &fields) {
        const uint64_t maxVal = std::numeric_limits<uint64_t>::max();
        for (const auto &deviceBlobList : blobLists) {
            for (const auto &blob : deviceBlobList.blobs) {
                if (blob.size > 0 && maxVal - fields.dataSize < blob.size) {
                    fields.dataSize = maxVal;
                } else {
                    fields.dataSize += blob.size;
                }
            }
        }
        fields.req.objectKey = FormatString("%s+count:%zu",
                                            keys.empty() ? "" : keys[0].substr(0, LOG_OBJECT_KEY_SIZE_LIMIT),
                                            keys.size());
    });
}
```

