当前 lambda 内又声明了一次 `keys`，容易混淆。建议直接在 lazy lambda 内从 `readParams` 构造：

```cpp
Raii raii([&accessPoint, &totalSize, &lastRc, readParams] {
    accessPoint.Record(lastRc, totalSize, [&](RequestParam &req) {
